<note n="0700004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0700004">經＋（一名弟子學有三輩）夾註【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0700005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0700005">〔月氏國居士〕－【宋】【宮】，月氏國居士＝月支優婆塞【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0700006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0700006">唯＝惟【三】【宮】</note>
